2. In the `componentDidMount()` lifecycle method of the `VideoCache` component, use the `fetch()` API to retrieve the video from the specified URL.
3. Use the `response.body` property of the `fetch()` API to create a new `ReadableStream` of the video.
4. Use the `ReadableStream.slice()` method to extract the first few seconds of the video.
